    "Details": "The UZL-8S variant trades all the weaponry of the -3S for a Streak SRM-6, Guardian ECM Suite, and a pair of Medium Pulse Lasers in each arm. The engine has been replaced with a smaller model, which reduces the 8S top speed to 86 km/h. However, eight Improved Jump Jets provide more mobility.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Cowl</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.04</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Upper, Right Upper</color>",
